---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Gaston Guitart.">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    Hi, this is Gaston GG. I write about distributed data systems: what it
    takes to move, store, and process large volumes of data reliably, and
    where the common wisdom on that breaks down in practice.
  </p>

  <blockquote>
    Outside of this, I read constantly, write my own music, and listen to
    even more of it, wide-ranging and rarely predictable.
  </blockquote>

  <p>
    Posts favor code and measurements over opinion. Where reasonable, the
    code behind a post lives in a public repo with tests, linked from the
    post itself.
  </p>
  <p>
    Feedback, corrections, and contributions are welcome. Open an issue or
    a PR on the relevant repo, reach out on <a href="https://github.com/ggasg">GitHub</a>, or email <a href="mailto:gaston.guitart@gmail.com">gaston.guitart@gmail.com</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    Post text is free to reuse and adapt under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">CC BY 4.0</a>, citation back to me is the only condition. Code, here and in linked repos, is <a href="https://github.com/ggasg/ggasg.github.io/blob/main/LICENSE">MIT</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
